\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Him. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ until the sun spreads\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  that they sinned before Me in the days of Hophni and Phinehas. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ your eyes 
\lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ are [like] doves\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  Your hues and your appearance and your characteristics are like those of a dove, 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ which cleaves to its mate, and when they slaughter it, it does not struggle but stretches forth its neck; 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ so have you offered your shoulder to bear My yoke and My fear. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ from within your kerchief; your 
\lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ hair is like a flock of goats\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  This praise is a paradigm of the praise of a woman beloved by her 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ bridegroom. Within your kerchief, your hair is beautiful and glistens with brilliance and whiteness like 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ the hair of white goats descending from the mountains, whose hair gleams in the distance. And in the 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ allegorical sense, [it is said of] the congregation of Israel that within your camps and your tents, even 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ the empty ones among you are as dear to Me as Jacob and his sons, who streamed down to descend 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ from Mount Gilead when Laban overtook them there. Another explanation: As those who mobilized 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ against Midian beyond the Jordan, which is in the land of Gilead, and this language is found in Midrash 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Shir Hashirim. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ within\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  Heb. \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ îÄáÌÇòÇã\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ . This is a term meaning “within,” for the majority of \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ áÌÀòÇã\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  in 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Scripture refers to something that covers and shields against something else, like (Job 9:7): “and He 
