\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Therefore, he says, \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ îÄáÌÇòÇã\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ . \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ your kerchief\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  Heb. \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ öÇîÌÈúÅêÀ\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ . An expression denoting a thing that confines 
